title: Claude Monet Water Lilies Apron
description:
Apron developed from Claude Monet’s Water Lilies, 1906 from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

This apron blends timeless style with modern practicality. If you like this, consider combining this with the Claude Monet Water Lilies Tea Towel and Pot Holder, for a special gift set.

  • Dimensions: 28 in. x 32 in. 
  • Material: 100% cotton
  • Machine wash, line dry.
